text: Dušan Houdek (born 2 April 1931) is a Czech former sports shooter. He competed in the 50 metre rifle, three positions and 50 metre rifle, prone events at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1931 births Category:Living people Category:Czech male sport shooters Category:Olympic shooters of Czechoslovakia Category:Shooters at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Bratislava
